@GameStore_HostAddress = http://localhost:5137
@token = paste-login-token-here

### View cart
GET {{GameStore_HostAddress}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add game to cart
POST {{GameStore_HostAddress}}/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### Update cart item quantity
PUT {{GameStore_HostAddress}}/cart/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 1
}

### Remove cart item
DELETE {{GameStore_HostAddress}}/cart/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Clear cart
DELETE {{GameStore_HostAddress}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Checkout
POST {{GameStore_HostAddress}}/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### My orders
GET {{GameStore_HostAddress}}/orders/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### My order details
GET {{GameStore_HostAddress}}/orders/my/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
